Name: Black Ido
About the game: Black ido is a super suit that can change gravity and protect the main character named TSK from falling from a great height. Feature of game: Adventure with the change of gravity Collecting coins Convenient control Challenging levels Physics, doors, keys and traps. In the game you have to change the gravity and use the geometry of the level to solve puzzles.
